survey_response.review_text: Annamalai sir is an extremely polite and knowledgeable doctor. He listens to your concerns. Examines and then gives you a clear picture of what the problem is and various options to solve it. He is also gives us option based on our financial situation. I had my wisdom tooth removed and the process was extremely professional and with negligible pain. I would recommend Annamalai sir 10/10 to anyone with any dental problems. **** **** ** **** * ****** *** ** ************** ****** *** ********

I had gone to Dr. Annamalai for my daughter's tooth alignment and was absolutely satisfied with the treatment.  He is so involved and dedicated and is passionate about his work and you will be amazed at the result.  This time I went for my teeth alignment and he was very patient in hearing me out fully.  He, after examining my x-ray advised me against the option and though disappointed that I had to live with my problem,  I  respect his advise as there is obviously no reason that he should advise me against it.  Doctors like Annamalai are very rare to find in these testing times and I am extremely happy to have found him. I wish him the very best in all his endeavors. God bless!
